{"tid":1611573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[解放台灣]  受港警開槍傷人影響，蔡英文民調大勝韓國瑜18.3%","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T04:39:35.000Z","uid":52658,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"48714c5a399c6042171c7fd58bfaf0692758cb1b","tid":1611573,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"2020總統大選將進入倒數百日決戰，根據綠黨與《94要客訴》合作所做最新總統大選民調<br />\n，蔡英文支持度50.9%，韓國瑜為32.6%，有16.5%受訪者尚未決定。針對韓國瑜的民調低<br />\n迷，韓幕僚、立委參選人孫大千表示「逆風」才是展現實力的時刻，呼籲韓粉展現信心、<br />\n勇氣與包容等三項堅持。<br />\n<br />\n這項最新總統選情民調顯示，蔡英文和韓國瑜的差距達到18.3%，在看好度部分，蔡英文<br />\n61%，韓國瑜25.8%；至於不分區政黨票部分，國民黨支持度34.5%，民進黨25.1%，台灣民<br />\n眾黨12.1%、時代力量8.1%、親民黨2.2%、綠黨1.8%、基進黨1.2%，國民黨獨佔鰲頭，領<br />\n先民進黨9.4%。<br />\n<br />\n這項民調時間是10月1日，採手機與市話各半，完成1021份樣本，在95%信心水準下，抽樣<br />\n誤差 &plusmn;3.07% 。"},{"pid":"f52b657ce37d25b39988e078e3adcc7d8fc51dd7","tid":1611573,"uid":271056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:56:00.000Z","msg":"We connected"},{"pid":"78d577498ca1c78c89ae72a707710fe28e1e403b","tid":1611573,"uid":52943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"本來冧橋都有機會挫一挫蔡貓奴支持度<br />\n港共popo開幾槍就抵消返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512d1ecfc5abc022a8140adcc3ae0a576d738f84","tid":1611573,"uid":149361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"歷史罪人 林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0269823ac888aa80294c8e792561a4630c4caa93","tid":1611573,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df79d114ca203a7ee5a5d12b46df9a4106e886b4","tid":1611573,"uid":289978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTim